name: OceansGallerie On SUI
description: OceansGallerie is a decentralized Web3 ecosystem on SUI that merges creativity, engagement, and rewards. It allows users to participate in AI-powered meme creation, task distribution, and community voting. Users earn $OCEANS tokens by completing creative tasks, which play a central role in the platform's ecosystem. The project aims to foster innovation and collaboration while empowering users to create value and grow within the decentralized space.
